                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Hay</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">White</persName>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1902-06-20">
                            <hi rend="italic">June 20, 1902</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Hay states that Mr. White may attend the funeral of the late King of Saxony,
                    to be held at Dresden, representing the President of the United States.)</p>
            </div>
